    <section id="section2">
        <h1>創帳號</h1>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-9">
                <span class="badge badge-ttl">API</span>
                <pre> <span class="label label-warning">GET</span> /signup</pre>

                <span class="badge badge-ttl">説明</span>
                <p>調用創帳號頁面創建 SG 會員帳號。帳號創建成功後，自動登入。</p>

                <span class="badge badge-ttl">範例</span>
                <pre>http://gameapi.smartgamesltd.com/signup</pre>

                <span class="badge badge-ttl">回傳</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>調用回傳頁面的 JavaScript 函式 <code>GetResult()</code> 來取得回傳結果，該函式回傳 JSON 字串。</li>
                    <li>例如<code>{"Code": 301, "Message": "ok"}</code>。</li>
                    <li>完整 Code 定義，<a href="/webapi-init#section5">請參看對照表</a>。</li>
                    <li>回傳 <a href="/webapi-init#SGMember">SGMember</a> 結構。</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-3">
                <span class="badge badge-ttl">WebView 頁面</span>
                <a href="<%= "assets/img/" + lang + "/pic08.png" %>" data-toggle="lightbox">
                    <img src="<%= "assets/img/" + lang + "/pic08.png" %>" class="img-responsive"/>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

