    <section id="section11">
        <h1>Token 快速登入</h1>

        <div class="row">
            <span class="badge badge-ttl">API</span>
            <pre> <span class="label label-warning">GET</span> <span class="label label-success">POST</span> /loginbytoken</pre>

            <span class="badge badge-ttl">説明</span>
            <p>使用 Token 快速登入，同時取得帳號資訊。</p>

            <span class="badge badge-ttl">範例</span>
            <pre>http://gameapi.smartgamesltd.com/loginbytoken?token=my_token</pre>

            <span class="badge badge-ttl">參數</span>
            <p>token：登入成功後取得。</p>

            <span class="badge badge-ttl">回傳</span>
            <ul>
                <li>回傳 <a href="/webapi-init#SGMember">SGMember</a> 格式JSON 字串。Code 1001 為登入成功，其它則為登入失敗。</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="section12">
        <h1>Session ID 登入驗證</h1>

        <div class="row">
            <span class="badge badge-ttl">API</span>
            <pre> <span class="label label-warning">GET</span> <span class="label label-success">POST</span> /verifysession</pre>

            <span class="badge badge-ttl">説明</span>
            <p>以 SessionID 取得登入帳號資訊。串接其他渠道二次登入驗證使用。</p>

            <span class="badge badge-ttl">範例</span>
            <pre>http://gameapi.smartgamesltd.com/verifysession?gamekey=my_gamekey&sessionid=my_sessionid&openid=my_openid&sign=my_sign</pre>

            <span class="badge badge-ttl">參數</span>
            <table class="table table-striped">
                <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>參數名稱</th>
                    <th>參數說明</th>
                </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>gamekey</td>
                    <td>開發者申請開通遊戲後取得的 gamekey。</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>openid</td>
                    <td>登入成功後取得的 openid。</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class>
                    <td>sessionid</td>
                    <td>登入成功後取得的 sessionID。</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>sign</td>
                    <td>以參數 gamekey, openid, sessionid 製作簽名字串。詳見 <a href="/server-sign#section2">簽名演算法</a>。</td>
                </tr>

                </tbody>
            </table>

            <span class="badge badge-ttl">回傳</span>
            <ul>
                <li>完整 Code 定義，<a href="/webapi-init#section5">請參看對照表</a>。</li>
                <li>回傳 <a href="/webapi-init#SGMember">SGMember</a> 結構。</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

